contents:
[package]
name = "accesskit"
version = "0.16.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "UI accessibility infrastructure across platforms"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["schemars", "serde"]

[dependencies.enumn]
version = "0.1.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.pyo3]
version = "0.20"
optional = true

[dependencies.schemars]
version = "0.8.7"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]
optional = true

[features]
enumn = ["dep:enumn"]
pyo3 = ["dep:pyo3"]
serde = ["dep:serde", "enumn"]
schemars = ["dep:schemars", "serde"]

[package]
name = "accesskit_atspi_common"
version = "0.9.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: core AT-SPI translation layer"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[features]
simplified-api = []

[dependencies]
serde = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0.39"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.24.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.atspi-common]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.zvariant]
version = "3"
default-features = false

[package]
name = "accesskit_consumer"
version = "0.24.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit consumer library (internal)"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[dependencies]
immutable-chunkmap = "2.0.5"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../common"

[package]
name = "accesskit_macos"
version = "0.17.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: macOS adapter"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
default-target = "x86_64-apple-darwin"

[dependencies]
once_cell = "1.13.0"
objc2 = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.24.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.2.0"
features = ["NSArray", "NSDictionary", "NSValue", "NSThread"]

[dependencies.objc2-app-kit]
version = "0.2.0"
features = ["NSAccessibility", "NSAccessibilityConstants", "NSAccessibilityElement", "NSAccessibilityProtocols", "NSResponder", "NSView", "NSWindow"]

[package]
name = "accesskit_unix"
version = "0.12.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: Linux adapter"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[features]
default = ["async-io"]
async-io = ["dep:async-channel", "dep:async-executor", "dep:async-task", "dep:futures-util", "atspi/async-std", "zbus/async-io"]
tokio = ["dep:tokio", "dep:tokio-stream", "atspi/tokio", "zbus/tokio"]

[dependencies]
futures-lite = "1.13"
serde = "1.0"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_atspi_common]
version = "0.9.0"
path = "../atspi-common"

[dependencies.atspi]
version = "0.19"
default-features = false

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "3.14"
default-features = false

[dependencies.async-channel]
version = "2.1.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-executor]
version = "1.5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-task]
version = "4.3.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.27"
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
version = "0.1.14"
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.32.0"
optional = true
features = ["macros", "net", "rt", "sync", "time"]

[package]
name = "accesskit_windows"
version = "0.22.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: Windows adapter"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[dependencies]
paste = "1.0"
static_assertions = "1.1.0"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.24.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.windows]
version = "0.54"
features = ["implement", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_System_Com", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Ole", "Win32_System_Variant", "Win32_UI_Accessibility", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging"]

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1.13.0"
scopeguard = "1.1.0"

[dev-dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
tag = "iced-xdg-surface-0.13-rc"

[package]
name = "accesskit_winit"
version = "0.22.0"
authors = ["The AccessKit contributors"]
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: winit adapter"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "accessibility", "winit"]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["winit/rwh_06", "winit/x11", "winit/wayland"]

[features]
default = ["accesskit_unix", "async-io", "rwh_06"]
rwh_06 = ["winit/rwh_06", "dep:rwh_06"]
async-io = ["accesskit_unix/async-io"]
tokio = ["accesskit_unix/tokio"]

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
tag = "iced-xdg-surface-0.13-rc"

[dependencies.rwh_05]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.5"
features = ["std"]
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_06]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6"
features = ["std"]
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.accesskit_windows]
version = "0.22.0"
path = "../windows"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.accesskit_macos]
version = "0.17.0"
path = "../macos"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"dragonfly\", target_os = \"freebsd\", target_os = \"openbsd\", target_os = \"netbsd\"))".dependencies.accesskit_unix]
version = "0.12.0"
path = "../unix"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
tag = "iced-xdg-surface-0.13-rc"
default-features = false
features = ["x11", "wayland", "wayland-dlopen", "wayland-csd-adwaita"]

[package]
name = "atomicwrites"
version = "0.4.2"
authors = ["Markus Unterwaditzer <markus-honeypot@unterwaditzer.net>"]
license = "MIT"
keywords = ["filesystem", "posix"]
readme = "README.md"
description = "Atomic file-writes."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/crate/atomicwrites"
homepage = "https://github.com/untitaker/rust-atomicwrites"
repository = "https://github.com/untitaker/rust-atomicwrites"
exclude = ["/.travis.yml", "/Makefile", "/appveyor.yml"]

[dependencies]
tempfile = "3.1"

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies.rustix]
version = "0.38.0"
features = ["fs"]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48.0"
features = ["Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Storage_FileSystem"]

[package]
name = "clipboard_macos"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the macOS clipboard"
license = "Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_macos"
keywords = ["clipboard", "macos"]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
default-target = "x86_64-apple-darwin"

[dependencies]
objc = "0.2"
objc_id = "0.1"
objc-foundation = "0.1"

[package]
name = "clipboard_wayland"
version = "0.2.2"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the clipboard of a Wayland window"
license = "Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_wayland"
keywords = ["clipboard", "wayland"]

[dependencies.smithay-clipboard]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/smithay-clipboard"
tag = "pop-dnd-5"
features = ["dnd"]

[dependencies.mime]
path = "../mime"

[dependencies.dnd]
path = "../dnd"

[package]
name = "clipboard_x11"
version = "0.4.2"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the X11 clipboard"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_x11"
keywords = ["clipboard", "x11"]

[dependencies]
x11rb = "0.13"
thiserror = "1.0"

[package]
name = "cosmic-client-toolkit"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.175"
bitflags = "2.9.3"

[dependencies.cosmic-protocols]
path = "../"

[dependencies.sctk]
package = "smithay-client-toolkit"
version = "0.20.0"

[dependencies.wayland-client]
version = "0.31.11"

[dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.32.9"
features = ["client", "staging"]

[dev-dependencies]
png = "0.18.0"
gbm = "0.18.0"

[dev-dependencies.wayland-backend]
version = "0.3.11"
features = ["client_system"]

[dev-dependencies.smithay]
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false
features = ["renderer_gl", "backend_drm"]

[features]
default = []

[package]
name = "cosmic-config"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"

[features]
default = ["macro", "subscription"]
dbus = ["dep:zbus", "cosmic-settings-daemon", "futures-util", "subscription"]
macro = ["cosmic-config-derive"]
subscription = ["iced_futures"]

[dependencies]
notify = "8.2.0"
ron = "0.11.0"
serde = "1.0.219"
dirs = "6.0.0"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.cosmic-settings-daemon]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/dbus-settings-bindings"
optional = true

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "5.11.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.atomicwrites]
git = "https://github.com/jackpot51/rust-atomicwrites"

[dependencies.calloop]
version = "0.14.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.cosmic-config-derive]
path = "../cosmic-config-derive/"
optional = true

[dependencies.iced]
path = "../iced/"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.iced_futures]
path = "../iced/futures/"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.47"
optional = true
features = ["time"]

[dependencies.async-std]
version = "1.13"
optional = true

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]
xdg = "3.0"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
known-folders = "1.3.1"

[package]
name = "cosmic-config-derive"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
syn = "2.0"
quote = "1.0"

[package]
name = "cosmic-freedesktop-icons"
version = "0.4.0"
edition = "2024"
license = "MIT"
description = "A Freedesktop Icons lookup crate"
repository = "https://github.com/pop-os/freedesktop-icons"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["icons", "gui", "freedesktop"]

[dependencies]
bstr = "1.12.1"
btoi = "0.5.0"
memchr = "2.7.6"
memmap2 = "0.9"
thiserror = "2.0"
xdg = "3.0"

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.41"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies]
speculoos = "0.13.0"
criterion = "0.7"

[features]
default = []
local_tests = []

[[bench]]
name = "simple_lookup"
harness = false

[package]
name = "cosmic-protocols"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
documentation = "https://pop-os.github.io/cosmic-protocols/"
repository = "https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-protocols"
authors = ["Victoria Brekenfeld <github@drakulix.de>"]
license = "GPL-3.0-only"
keywords = ["wayland", "client", "server", "protocol", "extension"]
description = "Generated API for the COSMIC wayland protocol extensions"
categories = ["gui", "api-bindings"]
readme = "README.md"

[dependencies]
wayland-scanner = "0.31.7"
wayland-backend = "0.3.11"
wayland-protocols-wlr = "0.3.9"
bitflags = "2.9"

[dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.32.9"
features = ["staging"]

[dependencies.wayland-client]
version = "0.31.11"
optional = true

[dependencies.wayland-server]
version = "0.31.10"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.wayland-backend]
version = "0.3.11"
features = ["client_system"]

[features]
default = ["client", "server"]
client = ["wayland-client", "wayland-protocols/client", "wayland-protocols-wlr/client"]
server = ["wayland-server", "wayland-protocols/server", "wayland-protocols-wlr/server"]

[workspace]
members = ["client-toolkit"]

[package]
name = "cosmic-settings-daemon"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "5.11.0"

[dev-dependencies]
futures = "0.3"

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dev-dependencies.zbus]
features = ["tokio"]
version = "5.11.0"

[package]
name = "cosmic-text"
description = "Pure Rust multi-line text handling"
version = "0.16.0"
authors = ["Jeremy Soller <jeremy@system76.com>"]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/cosmic-text/latest/cosmic_text/"
repository = "https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-text"
rust-version = "1.80"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["vi"]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2.4.1"
log = "0.4.20"
rangemap = "1.4.0"
self_cell = "1.0.1"
unicode-linebreak = "0.1.5"
unicode-script = "0.5.5"
unicode-segmentation = "1.10.1"

[dependencies.core_maths]
version = "0.1.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.cosmic_undo_2]
version = "0.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.fontdb]
version = "0.23"
default-features = false

[dependencies.harfrust]
version = "0.4.1"
default-features = false

[dependencies.hashbrown]
version = "0.16"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.libm]
version = "0.2.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.linebender_resource_handle]
version = "0.1.1"
default-features = false

[dependencies.modit]
version = "0.1.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.rustc-hash]
version = "1.1.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.skrifa]
version = "0.39.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.smol_str]
version = "0.2.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.syntect]
version = "5.1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.sys-locale]
version = "0.3.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.swash]
version = "0.2.0"
default-features = false
features = ["render", "scale"]
optional = true

[dependencies.unicode-bidi]
version = "0.3.13"
default-features = false
features = ["hardcoded-data"]

[features]
default = ["std", "swash", "fontconfig"]
fontconfig = ["fontdb/fontconfig", "std"]
monospace_fallback = []
no_std = ["hashbrown", "dep:libm", "skrifa/libm", "core_maths"]
peniko = []
shape-run-cache = []
std = ["fontdb/memmap", "fontdb/std", "harfrust/std", "linebender_resource_handle/std", "skrifa/std", "swash?/std", "sys-locale", "unicode-bidi/std"]
vi = ["modit", "syntect", "cosmic_undo_2"]
wasm-web = ["sys-locale?/js"]
warn_on_missing_glyphs = []

[[bench]]
name = "layout"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "text_shaping_benchmarks"
harness = false

[workspace]
members = ["examples/*"]

[dev-dependencies]
tiny-skia = "0.11.2"

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.5.1"
default-features = false
features = ["cargo_bench_support"]

[profile.test]
opt-level = 1

[package]
name = "cosmic-theme"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["test_all_features"]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]

[features]
default = ["export"]
export = ["serde_json"]
no-default = []

[dependencies]
almost = "0.2"
ron = "0.11.0"
dirs = "6.0.0"
thiserror = "2.0.16"

[dependencies.palette]
version = "0.7.6"
features = ["serializing"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.219"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.143"
optional = true
features = ["preserve_order"]

[dependencies.csscolorparser]
version = "0.7.2"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.cosmic-config]
path = "../cosmic-config/"
default-features = false
features = ["subscription", "macro"]

[package]
name = "dnd"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2.5.0"
raw-window-handle = "0.6"

[dependencies.mime]
path = "../mime"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"redox\"))))".dependencies.smithay-clipboard]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/smithay-clipboard"
tag = "pop-dnd-5"
features = ["dnd"]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"redox\"))))".dependencies.sctk]
package = "smithay-client-toolkit"
version = "0.19.1"
default-features = false
features = ["calloop"]

[package]
categories = ["gui"]
description = "Types for handling UI scaling"
edition = "2021"
keywords = ["DPI", "HiDPI", "scale-factor"]
license = "Apache-2.0"
name = "dpi"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-windowing/winit"
rust-version = "1.73"
version = "0.1.1"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["mint", "serde"]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]
targets = ["i686-pc-windows-msvc", "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc", "aarch64-apple-darwin", "x86_64-apple-darwin", "i686-unknown-linux-gnu", "x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu", "aarch64-apple-ios", "aarch64-linux-android", "wasm32-unknown-unknown"]

[features]
mint = ["dep:mint"]
serde = ["dep:serde"]

[dependencies.mint]
optional = true
version = "0.5.6"

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1"
features = ["serde_derive"]

[package]
name = "iced"
description = "A cross-platform GUI library inspired by Elm"
version = "0.14.0-dev"
edition = "2021"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>"]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = ["gui"]
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets"]
rust-version = "1.80"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]
all-features = true

[lints.rust]
unused_results = "deny"

[lints.clippy]
type-complexity = "allow"
semicolon_if_nothing_returned = "deny"
trivially-copy-pass-by-ref = "deny"
default_trait_access = "deny"
match-wildcard-for-single-variants = "deny"
redundant-closure-for-method-calls = "deny"
filter_map_next = "deny"
manual_let_else = "deny"
unused_async = "deny"
from_over_into = "deny"
needless_borrow = "deny"
new_without_default = "deny"
useless_conversion = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "forbid"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[features]
default = ["tiny-skia"]
wgpu = ["iced_renderer/wgpu", "iced_widget/wgpu"]
tiny-skia = ["iced_renderer/tiny-skia"]
image = ["image-without-codecs", "image/default"]
image-without-codecs = ["iced_widget/image", "dep:image"]
svg = ["iced_widget/svg"]
canvas = ["iced_widget/canvas"]
qr_code = ["iced_widget/qr_code"]
markdown = ["iced_widget/markdown"]
lazy = ["iced_widget/lazy"]
debug = ["iced_winit?/debug"]
tokio = ["iced_futures/tokio", "iced_accessibility?/tokio"]
async-std = ["iced_futures/async-std", "iced_accessibility?/async-io"]
smol = ["iced_futures/smol"]
system = ["iced_winit/system"]
web-colors = ["iced_renderer/web-colors"]
webgl = ["iced_renderer/webgl"]
highlighter = ["iced_highlighter", "iced_widget/highlighter"]
multi-window = ["iced_winit?/multi-window"]
advanced = ["iced_core/advanced", "iced_widget/advanced"]
fira-sans = ["iced_renderer/fira-sans"]
auto-detect-theme = ["iced_core/auto-detect-theme"]
strict-assertions = ["iced_renderer/strict-assertions"]
a11y = ["iced_accessibility", "iced_core/a11y", "iced_widget/a11y", "iced_winit?/a11y"]
winit = ["iced_winit", "iced_accessibility?/accesskit_winit"]
wayland = ["iced_widget/wayland", "iced_core/wayland", "iced_winit/wayland"]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]

rwh_06 = ["dep:rwh_06", "ndk/rwh_06"]
